rows.label: qev051511_MSG0001
rows.name:
...What's that? You wonder if I am hungry?
If I fought poorly because of it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051511_MSG0002
rows.name:
No. I ate much meat this morning.
I fought with all my strength.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051511_MSG0003
rows.name:
Which makes loss even worse!
I wanted prize money to buy more meat...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051511_MSG0004
rows.name:
Now you must win.
Then treat me to celebration feast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051511_MSG0005
rows.name:
Be wary. Strong fighter still waits for you.
But do not lose to any but me![ST:wait ]
